{"author":{"id":"b78c39e7b13f90a5827abfba043255fe7a4ede1499df23f110fffe5abfa44adc"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1770749881,"nonce":"qPe3ZF7EoWGmNZWA5Y/Xih2qhqc=","metadata":{"github-id":"I_kwDOQ241x87p1T4E","github-url":"https://github.com/rolker/ros2_agent_workspace/issues/181","origin":"github"},"title":"Consolidate agent documentation into self-contained framework entry points","message":"## Summary\n\nConsolidate agent documentation so each framework's entry point is self-contained with all rules inline. Currently agents must read 10+ files before they can start working — this creates indirection and context waste.\n\n## Problem\n\n- 135 files under `.agent/`\n- CLAUDE.md points to AI_RULES.md which points to rules/common/*.md which points to workflows/*.md\n- Agents forget rules they read early in the chain\n- Much of the content (workflows, skills, detailed CLI commands) is never used by real agents\n\n## Solution\n\nMake each framework's entry point self-contained:\n- **CLAUDE.md** (~150 lines): auto-loaded every Claude Code conversation, all rules inline\n- **copilot-instructions.md** (~150 lines): same treatment for Copilot\n- **gemini-cli.instructions.md** (~150 lines): same treatment for Gemini\n- **AI_RULES.md** (~40 lines): universal fallback for unknown agents\n\n## Phases\n\n1. Preserve test templates before deleting skills\n2. Rewrite CLAUDE.md as self-contained operational source of truth\n3. Expand other framework instruction files\n4. Trim AI_RULES.md to universal minimum\n5. Delete workflow, rule, and skill files (51 files)\n6. Delete support docs (8 files) + trim AGENT_ONBOARDING.md\n7. Update cross-references in surviving files\n8. Verification\n\n## What stays untouched\n\n- All scripts (`.agent/scripts/**`)\n- All hooks (`.agent/hooks/**`)\n- `.pre-commit-config.yaml`\n- `.agent/knowledge/` — ROS2 patterns and CLI best practices\n- `.agent/templates/` — issue plan, improvement issue templates\n- `.agent/WORKTREE_GUIDE.md`, `.agent/AI_IDENTITY_STRATEGY.md`, `.agent/WORKFORCE_PROTOCOL.md`\n- `.agent/work-plans/`, `.agent/scratchpad/`\n- `ARCHITECTURE.md`\n\n## Impact\n\n- **Before**: 135 files under `.agent/`, agents read 10+ docs before working\n- **After**: ~75 files, each agent reads 1 auto-loaded file with all rules inline\n- **Risk**: Low — all important rules preserved inline, all scripts/hooks/infrastructure untouched\n- **Related issues**: #178, #175, #145, #123, #103, #124, #132\n\n---\n**Authored-By**: `Claude Code Agent`\n**Model**: `Claude Opus 4.6`","files":null}]}